msgctxt "mn120:37.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saddhāya samannāgato hoti, sīlena … "
msgstr "Furthermore, take a mendicant who has faith, ethics, learning, generosity, and wisdom. "

