msgctxt "mn120:37.6"
msgid "‘aho vatāhaṃ āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihareyyan’ti. "
msgstr "‘If only I might realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this very life, and live having realized it with my own insight due to the ending of defilements.’ "

msgctxt "mn120:37.7"
msgid "So āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "They realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this very life. And they live having realized it with their own insight due to the ending of defilements. "

#. VAR: na katthaci upapajjatī”ti → na kuhiñci upapajjatīti (bj) | na katthaci uppajjati na kuhiñci uppajjatīti (pts1) | na kuhiñci upasampajja viharatīti. (mr)
msgctxt "mn120:37.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na katthaci upapajjatī”ti. "
msgstr "And, mendicants, that mendicant is not reborn anywhere.” "

